item.description:
Hi folks...are you set up for success in 2011? Have you gathered your power team to put you in the best position for success?

Ask yourself the following questions:

1. Are you saving as much money as possible on.....
....your telecom needs?....shopping?....dining?....entertainment....
dental?....vision....hearing...
2. Do you have unlimited, unbiased access to financial experts?
3. Is your identity protected?
4. Do you have convenient 24/7 access to health professionals?
5. Do you have a plan to pay off your debt in 1/2 to 1/3 of the time?
6. Do you have personal assistants to help you save time and money?
7. Do you have a plan to maximize your credit score?
8. Do you have unlimited access to a legal team?
9. Do you have a retirement solution that can work with any budget?
10. Do you have a Plan B, a way to make an additional stream of income?


10 am - Networking and overview
11 am - Business Training
Where: 1 Industrial Dr, Windham, NH

RSVP: Call Bernadette at 603-505-8683 or email at dette101@gmail.com
